  "layers": {
    "commentary": [
      {
        "id": "commentary-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 26,
          "end": 27
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "靡，無也。聖心無私，故視之若一也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 33,
          "end": 35
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "《書》曰：「知人則哲，惟帝其難之。」又曰：「旁求俊彥，啟迪後人。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 24,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "簪裾、珩珮所以別貴賤也。左思《蜀都賦》曰：「近則江漢炳靈，代載其英，蔚若相如忄爵，若君王。」《毛詩》曰：「嵩高惟嶽，峻極於天。惟嶽降神，生甫及申。」《春秋佐助期》曰：「漢將蕭何，昴精生於豐，通於製度也。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 3,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "《文子》曰：「知過萬人謂之英。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "蒞，臨也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 1,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "孔安國《尚書傳》曰：「美德曰彥。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 2
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "《易》曰：「聖人之大寶曰位。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "《書》曰：「咸懷忠良。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "《列女傳》曰：「文伯相魯，敬薑謂之曰：『吾語汝，理國之要，盡在經耳。夫服重任行遠，道正直而固者，軸也。軸可以為相。』文伯再拜，受教矣。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "《列女傳》曰：孟子之少也，既學而歸。孟母方織，問學所至矣。孟子曰：「自若也。」孟母以刀斷其織。孟子懼而問其故。旦夕勤學不息，師事子思，遂成天下之名儒。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 16,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "《論語》曰：「忠告以善道之。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 1,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "《穆天子傳》曰：「觀先王之策府。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 2,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "襟，心也。《毛詩》曰：「靜女其孌，貽我彤管。彤管有煒，悅懌女美。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 17,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "《論語》曰：「武王曰：『予有亂臣十人。』」鄭玄曰：「亂，治也。武王言我有治政事者十人。謂文母、周公、召公、太公、畢公、榮公、太顛、閎夭、散宜生、南宮括也。」",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 19,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "謂伊尹、傅說也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
